{"tid":245093,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【Bitcoin WannaCry】黑客指定贖金拖累 Bitcoin單日跌逾一成","createTime":"2017-05-16T03:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T17:49:48.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed0f22bfe1a00d080e281cd6e19480196689f05","tid":245093,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/112240_0c68dc0f5e54e7a5d3cbbda3bc98ab08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F112240_0c68dc0f5e54e7a5d3cbbda3bc98ab08.jpg&h=cf674b31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橫掃全球的黑客要求各電腦使用者以Bitcoin交付贖金，涉及逾20萬部電腦，但這個負面消息影響連日炒高的Bitcoin，拖累由1,848美元急跌至1,644美元，目前最新報1,685美元，跌了足足200美元。<br />\n<br />\n同時由於日圓需求輕微減少，中國成交量增加，令Bitcoin價格在單日內大幅浮動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56699053&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56699053%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170516&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b14a1e63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56699053%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170516&h=d9b5bbf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56699053&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170516</a>"},{"pid":"bf3fdbf2d198e3429ab50f843b8d5b67f9b0f4e9","tid":245093,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:25:52.000Z","msg":"唔係應該多左人換bitcoin bitcoin會升咩<br />\n<br />\n點解跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135f304a08fbcb63cd48ca7e2ad0fe1d20794914","tid":245093,"uid":34976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T09:30:44.000Z","msg":"